item.title: About me
item.description: My name is EinsKatze, also known as Pascal, and I am currently undergoing an apprenticeship as an IT specialist for system integration. Im into linux and privacy, but overall i really like all kinds of tech. As you may have already noticed from my other profiles such as discord or github, i really like cats. Keep an eye out for future updates to this page.
